Changes:
 jm-util (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   [ Jan Matějka ]
   * fix(build): make image
   * fx: recurse make check
   * rf: add git-cif module
   * fx(git-cif): make git commit with un-edited template
   * ft(git-cif): git-cif is a superset of git-commit
   * fx(git-cif): handle case when lcpp is empty and run in single commit
   * rf(git-cif/jm-cif1.zsh): use -m instead of -F
   * fx(git-cif/jm-cif1.zsh): override EDITOR only if set to vim
   * ft(git-cif): -d does not open EDITOR by default
   * ft(jm-alias/jm-alias.cpp): grep exclude *.pyc
   * ft(jm-alias/jm-alias.cpp): grep --color=auto
   * fx(#build): dev build - key file name
   * fx(#build): install zsh_comp_dir
   * rf(#build): identify modules by file name .mod in the mod tree
   * ft(versionator): initial implementation
   * ft(#build): integrate versionator
